    public class HwPLDImpl
extends HwComputingResourceImpl
implements HwPLD
    An implementation of the model object 'Hw PLD'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Technology
    • Organization
    • Nb LU Ts
    • Nd LUT Inputs
    • Nb Flip Flops
    • Blocks RAM
    • Blocks Computing
